uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.serial

Class IInstanceParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.serial.FSerialiser
      • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.serial.IInstanceParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FSerialiserVocab, ISerialiserVocab

    public class IInstanceParser
extends FSerialiser
implements ISerialiserVocab
    Parser for the standard XML serialisation of MEKON instances as represented via IFrame/ISlot networks.

    If any updates have occured to the model since an instance was serialised which prevent the instance from being reassembled in its orignial form, the instance will be partially assembled as far as the updates allow, and provided together with information as to the pruning that was required.
